y hair systems for 30 years and with covid, their factory's lead time has gone into 8 months and I am still waiting for 3 units I've already paid for. After extensive research on hair company's, I came across Lavivid and they have by far exceeded my expectations. The quality of the hair and base on the skin poly unit is perfect. I ordered a stock system first to try them out and have now gotten my custom order with only a 2 month lead time. I just reordered two more custom units so I am ahead of the game. I highly recommend them and Tina in the customer service department is great at answering all of your questions and concerns. I always get a response back within 24 hours through email. You will not be disapointed!<\/p>\n<\/div>\n        <\/div><\/li>\n\n        <li><div class=\"sub-box\">\n            <div class=\"top-sellers-comment-pic\"><div>\n                <strong style=\"background-color: #ceffc9;\">MA<\/strong>\n                <span>Massimo<\/span>\n<\/div><\/div>\n            <div class=\"top-sellers-comment-content\">\n                <div class=\"top-sellers-comment-date\">\n                    <img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/customer-show20220913\/ico_stars.png\" alt=\"stars\" width=\"108\" height=\"20\" class=\"ico_stars\" data-src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/customer-show20220913\/ico_stars.png\">\n                    <span>March 11, 2022<\/span>\n                <\/div>\n                <strong class=\"top-sellers-comment-content-sttl\">Amazing quality<\/strong>\n                <p>I've started losing my hair since the age of 19, as you can imagine it was a big hit on my confidence, when you are so young you have too many things to worry about, and hair loss is something you really don't want to add to that list. I started using medication (minoxidil and finisteride) but they stopped working, and at the age of 24 I decided to undergo to a hair transplant. Every thing was going great until I started to lose my hair again and that's where I noticed that the HT was botched and I couldn't even shave my hair due to the scars left by the surgeon. I started using copious amount of concealers to cover my bald spots until I finally took the decision to try hair systems. I honestly have to say that it wasn't an easy journey. The first one I had was a junky and faulty rug provided by an hair saloon that charged me a fortune. I hated it so much that I changed it after a month and a half. The second one was from an online shop and still wasn't good enough, the hair was coarse and dry and it looked fake. I was about to give up until I came across LAVIVID HAIR, and it was a game changer! My first unit was Helios, full Swiss lace, and I could immediately notice the amazing quality of the hair, and master craftsmanship that goes on making those pieces. Soft hair, easy to style and to maintain and very natural hairline. I am currently wearing a Mirage thin skin poly and I can just say that I LOVE IT! I can style my hair however I want (even if I love my right parted quiff and I stick with that), the hairline is so undetectable and is a peace of mind. It's easy to maintain so it suits my lifestyle and it rarely tangles.<br>I can certainly say that I'll be a LaVivid Hair customer from now on and I'll never change it.<br>Thank you!<\/p>\n<\/div>\n        <\/div><\/li>\n\n        <li><div class=\"sub-box\">\n            <div class=\"top-sellers-comment-pic\"><div>\n                <strong style=\"background-color: #c9e1ff;\">J<\/strong>\n                <span>Ángel J Martínez<\/span>\n<\/div><\/div>\n            <div class=\"top-sellers-comment-content\">\n                <div class=\"top-sellers-comment-date\">\n                    <img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/customer-show20220913\/ico_stars.png\" alt=\"stars\" width=\"108\" height=\"20\" class=\"ico_stars\" data-src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/cus